<h2 style="text-align: left;">
  <strong>Agent Guide – Return for Credit (R4C)</strong>
</h2>
<h1>Pre-Requisites:</h1>
<p>To login as an agent, we should have Sandbox access for the required test environment. We have two types of Agents L1 &amp; L2. L1 Agent can login to the Sandbox URL and create a Return Request for Stock Rotation. L2 Agent can view the cases assigned to them and can change the case owner.</p>
<p>
  <strong>Sandbox (IAOQA) Link: </strong>
  <a href="https://isvc--isvcqa25.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/">
    <strong>https://isvc--isvciaoqa.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/</strong>
  </a>Access related issues, Contact: <span>@Indus ISVC GRL R4C</span>
</p>
