<h3>Note: Embargo check(GTS Screening):</h3>
<ul>
  <li data-uuid="b3d5ca18-535d-4bb3-b725-f12c66a44ea8">When agent clicks on ‘Next’ button or ‘Save for Later’, Country values from both ‘Return to Customer’ and ‘Collection’ addresses are sent to ‘Embargo GTS API’ to check if selected country is in ‘Embargo list’.</li>
  <li data-uuid="13559013-a22e-4bfd-8857-24b23e872b5b">If a country is an embargo country, that respective address would be a hard stop and agent would be notified by error toast message with details.</li>
  <li data-uuid="031f9bf0-5369-41c9-8ee3-020c787bbb07">If both countries pass GTS screening, then agent would be redirected to the next stage or case detail page respectively.</li>
  <li data-uuid="0faf0e71-5eb9-46a4-bf4e-421e953efcf8">When agent clicks on ‘Next’ button or ‘Save for Later’, Country values from ‘Return to Customer’, ‘Collection’, ‘Sold to address’, ‘Ship to Address’ and ‘Payer’ addresses are validated from local database check.</li>
  <li data-uuid="6273d863-4a90-49ff-8100-5ae7f7d5b409">If a country is an embargo country, that respective address would be a hard stop and agent would be notified by error toast message with details.</li>
  <li data-uuid="e8146b1d-fa39-4183-8b60-91e37a30c3e7">If all the countries pass GTS screening, then agent would be redirected to the next stage or case detail page respectively.</li>
