  <li data-uuid="75c81841-e1a1-4d52-a7b5-c7c6afd19239">Onclick of PO History Button, we will be validating MRB Reference numbers in salesforce data base.</li>
  <li data-uuid="8d33c895-88ff-4662-a420-180130a7895d">The entered MRB Ref number should match with the product MRB number.</li>
  <li data-uuid="1523ae16-1347-496c-962d-fe9f892c2963">The ‘Valid From’ and ‘Valid To’ dates should be in the current date range.</li>
  <li data-uuid="b4c1c206-bc01-4e4f-aa1f-a2cc775d6cb0">If the ‘Valid To’ date is empty, it will be considered default date as ‘9999-12-31’</li>
  <li data-uuid="9c46b5e5-8898-403e-bc90-f6869815f32b">The invalid MRB Reference number of the line items will be disabled in the UI and displayed the error message in ‘i’ icon.</li>
  <li data-uuid="b885dceb-eb13-4038-8366-d7516a74da27">The Valid MRB Reference number of the line items will be validating in POH API to get the PO numbers.</li>
  <li data-uuid="a682f9e7-8b43-4d8f-8c85-d8fca750a177">If the line is having PO number from the step 1(PO search / Validate PO), here we will bypass PO history API call just validate the date range</li>
