  <li data-uuid="f3b3333b-cdd6-4b9a-b4f2-e8db9f89163d">Here agent can see all the case details briefly and confirm if everything is correct before he can submit the case.</li>
</ul>
<p>
  <span>
    <ac:image>
      <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-7_15-26-59-1.png"/>
