</p>
<ul>
  <li data-uuid="a481a386-b149-4c93-a4a0-c8b6ace1f8d8">Agent can see “Edit”, “Cancel” and “Submit” buttons.</li>
  <li data-uuid="079fe742-fe2b-4cf0-be45-16ba447862f3">In case of any soft blocks (SAP blocks or other), ‘Submit’ button will be disabled and agent would be notified by a toast message about the presence of soft blocks.</li>
  <li data-uuid="3d39658d-9f34-4671-9d79-dac613189784">Then agent can edit the case again or continue and submit the case if no soft blocks are present.</li>
  <li data-uuid="4444344b-3bf3-4dc6-9653-e5fdbd31789c">If the Net Value is greater than 100k or total price overridden for line items is greater than 25k then case status will be ‘Pending Approval’.</li>
  <li data-uuid="ac5ac1e9-83c4-44bd-8584-84e952601b1f">If the Net Value is less than 100k and total price overridden for line items is less than 25k then case status will be ‘RMA Authorized’.</li>
  <li data-uuid="be925a14-eaf2-452d-b106-e2888bf3e9a3">On click of Submit button, the case is submitted with case status as ‘Pending Approval’ or ‘RMA Authorized’ agent is redirected to the ‘Case Detail Page’.</li>
  <li data-uuid="25dce824-1553-4a12-ba38-6bab4fb32a17">If agent clicks on cancel then the case is saved with “Draft” status and agent is redirected to the related ‘Case Detail Page’.</li>
</ul>
