<ul>
  <li data-uuid="adcabf3e-16ed-4a36-a474-d4a8b6537af9">If agent selects ‘delete’, then he will be shown a prompt to confirm if he really wants to delete the line item.</li>
  <li data-uuid="a4c74fed-7bbb-475f-ae50-8403aaf91bd7">Agent can also unselect the line items which will have same functionality as selecting ‘Delete’ status.</li>
