<ul>
  <li data-uuid="26a868b9-7702-420f-b752-c6cbf4dcdad4">
    <strong>For Pending Approval Cases, </strong>Only Collection Date field can be edited, and we can’t edit anything else.</li>
  <li data-uuid="6f33d42e-e0a0-4171-aadf-dbc21a9b6be3">In Edit Case scenario, for any line item, if the earlier entitlement check date is on same day, we will not be doing the Entitlement check for that Line item again and we use earlier data but if any new line items are added then the Entitlement check API callout will happen for the newly added Line Items.</li>
  <li data-uuid="da935998-a25c-4f66-a510-39de29d1277e">If case is being edited and the earlier and line items are gone beyond Credit Price Validation step and earlier detected credit price is on same day, then credit price validation API call is bypassed for existing line items.</li>
</ul>
